<div id="edition" style="display:none; margin-top: 0px;"></div>

<div id="sub-main" >
	<div id="wiki-content-block">

	
		


<p><strong>Ritual Spear Fragment</strong> is a <a class="wiki_link" href="/Consumables">Consumable</a> in Dark Souls 3. It is part of <a class="wiki_link" title="" href="/The+Ringed+City" target="">The Ringed City</a> <a class="wiki_link" title="" href="/DLC" target="">DLC</a>.</p> 
<div id="infobox" class="infobox"> 
 <div class="table-responsive"> 
  <table class="wiki_table"> 
   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;"> <h3>Ritual Spear Fragment</h3> </td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/file/Dark-Souls-3/ritual_spear_fragment.png" width="100"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td><br> 
      <blockquote> 
       <p>Online play item.<br>A fragment of the matching ritual spears once held by the knights of Princess Filianore.</p> 
       <p>They are the namesake of the Spears of the Church.</p> 
       <p>When Spears of the Church face unduly treacherous foes, this allows them to draw upon former majesty, and summon a row of upward-thrusting ritual spears.</p> 
      </blockquote> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 id="toc0" class="bonfire"><a name="x--Green Blossom Usage"></a>Ritual Spear Fragment Usage</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Summon a row of upwardly thrusting ritual spears.</li> 
 <li>Gives the player poise when used</li> 
 <li>Can only be used if the Player is summoned as a member of <a class="wiki_link" title="" href="/Spears+of+the+Church" target="">Spears of the Church</a></li> 
 <li>When used the player can either be surrounded or "throw" the fragment just before them to summon upward thrusting ritual spears that deal lightning damage to foes. Spears will persist for a few seconds before disappearing. An additional line of spears will appear in the direction of when the item was originally used, not the direction of the player after using the item.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 id="toc1" class="bonfire"><a name="x--Green Blossom Locations"></a>Ritual Spear Fragment Locations</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Can be found behind the Spears of the Church Shrine. Which is just before the Cathedral Ringed knight.</li> 
 <li>From the Shared Grave Bonfire run up the path into the church. Once there take the stairs up on your left. Kill or run past the Ringed Knight in front of you and on the back of the Monument.<a class="wiki_link" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qhY3HIL1FTI"> Video Location</a></li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 id="toc2" class="bonfire"><a name="x--Notes"></a>Notes</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Summoned spears can be aimed</li> 
 <li>The spears can be used both offensively and defensively&nbsp;</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 id="toc3" class="bonfire"><a name="x--Trivia"></a>Trivia</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Trivia goes here</li> 
</ul> 
